25\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1893\" height=\"913\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A screenshot showing the Black Notepad app in Microsoft Store\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-black-notepad-app-in-microsoft-store.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt is available for free in the Microsoft Store, so you can download and start using it quickly. Alternatively, you can check online for other options with advanced functionality, like \u003ca href=\"https://notepad-plus-plus.org/downloads/v8.7.7/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNotepad++\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"how-to-enable-dark-mode-in-notepad-on-windows-11\"\u003e\n                        How to Enable Dark Mode in Notepad on Windows 11\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt’s even easier to enable dark mode in Notepad on Windows 11. Alternatively, you can also \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/windows-11-dark-mode/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eenable and customize dark mode\u003c/a\u003e on your laptop, which will usually affect multiple apps across the OS.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"modify-the-notepad-settings\"\u003e\n            Modify the Notepad Settings\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eUnlike Windows 10, Windows 11 allows you to change the theme of the Notepad app directly from its settings.\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Launch Notepad and click the gear icon in the top-right corner.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        In the \u003cstrong\u003eSettings\u003c/strong\u003e menu, click on \u003cstrong\u003eApp theme\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Select \u003cstrong\u003eDark\u003c/strong\u003e from the available options.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1398\" height=\"568\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The three theme options in the Notepad Settings app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-three-theme-options-in-the-notepad-settings-app.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis should successfully enable dark mode in Notepad. If you\u0026#39;d prefer to have your theme change automatically based on your system settings, proceed to the next method. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"use-the-settings-app\"\u003e\n            Use the Settings App\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eNotepad offers three theme options: Light, Dark, and Use system setting. If Notepad is set to follow the system theme, changing your device’s system theme will automatically adjust Notepad\u0026#39;s appearance. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eHere\u0026#39;s how to enable dark mode system-wide via the Windows Settings app:\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Press \u003cstrong\u003eWin + I\u003c/strong\u003e to open the Settings app.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Navigate to \u003cstrong\u003ePersonalization\u003c/strong\u003e from the left-hand menu.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Click \u003cstrong\u003eColors\u003c/strong\u003e in the next window.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Expand the dropdown for \u003cstrong\u003eChoose your mode\u003c/strong\u003e and select \u003cstrong\u003eDark\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1007\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A screenshot showing the three color modes in the Windows Settings app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-three-color-modes-in-the-windows-settings-app.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eNow, launch Notepad to confirm that dark mode is enabled.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo undo these changes, simply repeat the steps above and select \u003cstrong\u003eLight\u003c/strong\u003e from the theme options. If you encounter issues switching back to light mode, refer to \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/windows-device-stuck-dark-mode/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eour guide on troubleshooting Windows devices stuck in dark mode\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"how-to-enable-dark-theme-in-notepad\"\u003e\n                        How to Enable Dark Theme in Notepad++\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNotepad++ is like the classic Windows app but with some advanced functionality. This third-party text editor expands on the functionality of the classic Notepad by offering features like syntax highlighting, macros, and plugins. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eHere’s how you can enable the dark theme in Notepad++:\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Open Notepad++ and navigate to \u003cstrong\u003eSettings\u003c/strong\u003e \u0026gt; \u003cstrong\u003eStyle Configurator\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        In the \u003cstrong\u003eSelect theme\u003c/strong\u003e dropdown menu, choose \u003cstrong\u003eDeep Black\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Customize the app further by adjusting styles, fonts, or colors if desired.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Once done, click \u003cstrong\u003eSave \u0026amp; Close\u003c/strong\u003e. \n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1917\" height=\"1004\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A screenshot showing the Style Configurator Settings displayed in Notepad++ which is in dark mode\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/a-screenshot-showing-the-style-configurator-settings-displayed-in-notepad-which-is-in-dark-mode.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYour Notepad++ interface should now be in dark mode. To revert to the default theme, follow the same steps and select Default (stylers.xml) instead.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThere are many reasons to use dark mode in Notepad and Notepad++, but the simplest is that it often feels easier on the eyes. Of course, there\u0026#39;s also an argument to be made for \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/dont-use-dark-mode-on-your-phone/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ewhy you shouldn\u0026#39;t use dark mode on your device\u003c/a\u003e, so I recommend trying out both options and seeing which works best for you.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
